Name: Lightbox Gallery Generator

Author: Nader Chehab

Date: June 25, 2011

Requirements: Python version 3.2

License: Creative Commons Attribution 3.0 Unported License.

How to use:

Edit GalleryGenerator.xml to setup the configuration. Default settings should work fine.

To run on windows: Edit Run.bat and set the correct path to python.exe then run it or simply type:
python __init__.py

To run on linux with a shell command:
./__init__.py


This will create:
- an html file (portfolio.html by default) which was generated according to the template (PortfolioTemplate.html by default)
- a folder of resized images + their thumbnails inside the portfolio folder. The source of these images is the 'source' folder, by default.
